00:40:17,510 --> 00:40:18,310
Saya melukis ini

783
00:40:18,310 --> 00:40:19,680
berdasarkan rupa gadis

784
00:40:19,680 --> 00:40:20,680
dalam mimpi saya.

785
00:40:21,230 --> 00:40:22,430
